//AV1:
//P3: 60 melee, 30 antihorse, 32 archers, 48 mounted
//P4: 27 melee, 27 antihorse, 24 archers, 18 mounted
//P5: 54 mounted
//P6: 60 mounted
//P7: 54 mounted
//P8: 48 melee, 24 antihorse, 32 archers, 36 mounted
//P9: 24 mounted
//P10: 24 melee, 12 antihorse, 24 archers, 18 mounted
//P11: 60 melee, 36 antihorse, 24 archers
//P12: 24 mounted
//P16: 72 mounted

//AV2:
//P3: 48 mounted
//P4: 54 mounted
//P5: 54 mounted
//P6: 60 mounted
//P7: 54 mounted
//P8: 108 mounted
//P9: 24 mounted
//P10: 27 mounted
//P11: 99 mounted
//P12: 24 mounted
